version_description: This song is in the key of A.
Follows exactly what the band played when they showed an acoustic version.

My version have way better formatting than the other one. Every section in my tab is named properly and there is enough space between each section as well, this makes the tab easier so read and understand.
This version consists of basic chords and is according to the official music video (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o5fuqdczxEE).

This is in the correct key, and includes a properly tabbed out guide for playing the intro bassline which can also function as the main verse riff (which is not offered in other chord tabs on the site), in addition this chord tab provides the proper progression for the verse  as well as the chorus (which the other chord tab fails to do)
